texts.content: {"text":"الٓر ۚ تِلْكَ ءَايَٰتُ ٱلْكِتَٰبِ وَقُرْءَانٍۢ مُّبِينٍۢ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.91764706373214722,0.76470589637756348,0.54901963472366333]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,56]}]}

{"text":"ذَرْهُمْ يَأْكُلُوا۟ وَيَتَمَتَّعُوا۟ وَيُلْهِهِمُ ٱلْأَمَلُ ۖ فَسَوْفَ يَعْلَمُونَ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.91764706373214722,0.76470589637756348,0.54901963472366333]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,83]}]}

{"text":"وَمَآ أَهْلَكْنَا مِن قَرْيَةٍ إِلَّا وَلَهَا كِتَابٌۭ مَّعْلُومٌۭ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.91764706373214722,0.76470589637756348,0.54901963472366333]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,67]}]}

{"text":"مَّا تَسْبِقُ مِنْ أُمَّةٍ أَجَلَهَا وَمَا يَسْتَـْٔخِرُونَ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.91764706373214722,0.76470589637756348,0.54901963472366333]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,59]}]}

{"text":"وَقَالُوا۟ يَٰٓأَيُّهَا ٱلَّذِى نُزِّلَ عَلَيْهِ ٱلذِّكْرُ إِنَّكَ لَمَجْنُونٌۭ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.91764706373214722,0.76470589637756348,0.54901963472366333]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,79]}]}

{"text":"لَّوْ مَا تَأْتِينَا بِٱلْمَلَٰٓئِكَةِ إِن كُنتَ مِنَ ٱلصَّٰدِقِينَ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.91764706373214722,0.76470589637756348,0.54901963472366333]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,67]}]}

{"text":"مَا نُنَزِّلُ ٱلْمَلَٰٓئِكَةَ إِلَّا بِٱلْحَقِّ وَمَا كَانُوٓا۟ إِذًۭا مُّنظَرِينَ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.91764706373214722,0.76470589637756348,0.54901963472366333]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,82]}]}

{"text":"إِنَّا نَحْنُ نَزَّلْنَا ٱلذِّكْرَ وَإِنَّا لَهُۥ لَحَٰفِظُونَ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.91764706373214722,0.76470589637756348,0.54901963472366333]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,62]}]}

{"text":"وَلَقَدْ أَرْسَلْنَا مِن قَبْلِكَ فِى شِيَعِ ٱلْأَوَّلِينَ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.91764706373214722,0.76470589637756348,0.54901963472366333]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,58]}]}

{"text":"كَذَٰلِكَ نَسْلُكُهُۥ فِى قُلُوبِ ٱلْمُجْرِمِينَ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[0.91764706373214722,0.76470589637756348,0.54901963472366333]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":10,"useLetterColor":true,"range":[0,48]}]}
